HEADWORD: Nymphalidae
<hw>Nymphalidae</hw> <pos>prop. n.</pos> <def>A natural family of large
beautifully colored butterflies, called also the <altname>brush-footed
butterflies</altname>; formerly called <fam>Nymphales</fam>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> family <fam>Nymphalidae</fam>.</syn>⟦br⟧
